/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/25\/six-huquq-maruf-for-muslims\/","url_meta":{"origin":15443,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Six rights of good conduct for a Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA\u00a0Muslim has six rights over another Muslim in good conduct: to greet him with peace when he meets him, to respond to his invitation, to respond to his sneeze, to visit him when he\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/20\/iftar-dates-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":15443,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Iftar: Breaking fast with dates and water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you breaks his fast, let him break it with dates for they are blessed. If they are not found, let him break it with water for it is pure.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14615,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/06\/dua-tashahhud-allah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":15443,"p